events.name: アイテム屋自宅外出ドア

parameters: \N<Item Shop Owner>Hmm... What should I do...

\N<Item Shop Owner>Ah, I'm sorry, customer. I have a bit of a
problem...

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Oh, is that so? \.I am a knight, but if you'd
like, I can listen to your story.
\CE[79]\N<Item Shop Owner>Oh, knight! That's reliable! Please, listen to me!

\N<Item Shop Owner>The package I ordered the other day is supposed to
arrive today, but it seems that a large number of
monsters have appeared on the \C[17]Yakumo
Highway\C[0], where the carriage is supposed to
pass, and they are blocking the road.
\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Monsters!? That's a big problem, isn't it?

\CE[79]\N<Item Shop Owner>That package is a specially ordered important
item, you know. I just can't stand the thought of
it being destroyed by monsters...!

\N<Item Shop Owner>I even consulted with the guards at the barracks,
but they said they're too busy to deal with it
right away. I don't care who does it anymore, I
just want someone to take care of it!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Understood, I will go and handle it! \.I will
definitely do something about it, so please wait
calmly.

\CE[79]\N<Item Shop Owner>The fate of the shop depends on this! I'm counting
on you!

I can now go to the 'Grassy Plains' from the world
map.

\N<Item Shop Owner>Before my important merchandise gets destroyed,
please exterminate the monsters!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Hey, it's you! You took care of the monsters on
the highway, right?
\N<Item Shop Owner>The goods have arrived safely. Thank you!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Alright, with this the shop will prosper again! I
need to start preparing right away!
\OC[31]\N<Rain>Well then, I'll take my leave now.

\CE[79]\N<Item Shop Owner>Ah, if you need anything, I'll provide it as a
service. So please come to my shop when you're in
need!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Thanks to you, I'm currently preparing the goods
that arrived. Look forward to it!
\N<Item Shop Owner>Oh, it's you! Thanks for last time!

\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>No, please don't worry. It was just something
natural for a knight to do.

\N<Item Shop Owner>Well, I'm grateful. Sorry for asking you to do
something inconvenient again, but there's one more
thing I'd like to ask. I'm facing a little trouble
again...

\OC[31]\N<Rain>What is it? If I can be of help, I'll assist you
as much as possible, but...

\CE[79]\N<Item Shop Owner>Well, actually, the new product that was safely
stocked thanks to you didn't sell as well as I had
hoped.

\N<Item Shop Owner>There's no doubt about the quality of the
product... In fact, it's top-notch! \. That's why
I'm thinking of coming up with a creative way to
promote it.

\N<Item Shop Owner>So, I want you to be the model! When it comes to
this kind of thing, it's best to have a beautiful
person appeal for it!

\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Eh... Are you saying that you want me to do the
promotion?

\N<Item Shop Owner>That's right. But all I'm asking you to do is wear
the product and let me take a photo. Then we'll
make it into posters and display them.

\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>By the way, what kind of product is it in the
first place?

\CE[79]\N<Item Shop Owner>To put it simply, it's equipment for adventurers.
It's lightweight because it's engraved with magic,
but it can still protect you well and is both
light and durable.

\N<Item Shop Owner>If a knight who protects the country could appeal
for it, the image would be quite good. And
besides, you're quite beautiful and have a great
figure, so I think it would suit you very well.
It'll work, it'll work!

\N<Item Shop Owner>That's why I'm asking you, it'll just be taking
photos so it'll be over quickly!

\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(I did say I would help as much as possible...
Well, if it's just taking photos, I guess it's
fine...)

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I understand. However, this time is special, you
know.

\N<Item Shop Owner>Alright! I'll take you up on that favor! \. Hurry
up and get changed! I'll start taking the photos
right away, so come around to the back!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Well then, please put this on! You can use the
room over there to change.
\OC[31]\N<Rain>W-Will I have to wear something like this...?

\N<Item Shop Owner>Oh... just as I thought! Nice! It suits you so
well!!
\N<Item Shop Owner>Ah, it's the best! A masterpiece!

\CE[77]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Um... Is this not meant to be worn over something?
I think it's a bit too revealing, don't you
think...?

\CE[79]\N<Item Shop Owner>Don't be silly, it's a bikini armor, so of course
it is!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Lightweight, durable, and easy to move in! It's
also great for dealing with the heat and has
excellent versatility!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Above all, it's incredibly sexy! The contradiction
of being armor with a lot of exposure! The
coexistence of hardness and softness, two opposing
concepts!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Because it's easy to put on and take off, you can
seduce others in your natural state when the time
comes! It's a perfect equipment that combines
functionality and sensuality! It's a product full
of benefits for female adventurers, don't you
think?

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>I don't think there's a need to become a seductive
figure in the dungeon... In fact, this outfit is
embarrassing even before considering its
functionality...

\N<Item Shop Owner>That's just a matter of getting used to it! Once
you experience the benefits of this high-
functionality, you'll forget all about those
concerns!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Hey, let's take a picture! Once everyone sees your
photo, they'll all want to try it on too!!

\N<Item Shop Owner>Good, good...! This is great! I'm getting
excited...!

\CE[78]\CE[79]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(The aura of desire...! \.──── I see, so this
outfit is a product of his desires...)

\CE[78]\CE[79]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(It seems like I have no choice but to let him
take pictures until he's satisfied...)

\CE[79]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(I never thought I would end up in such a lewd
outfit... but... I've made up my mind. Let's
finish this as quickly as possible...)

\N<Item Shop Owner>Alright, are you ready? Then, for now, try
striking a pose however you like!

\CE[78]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>E-even if you say 'strike a pose'... what should I
do...?

\N<Item Shop Owner>Hmm, then why don't you try raising both elbows
like this and sticking your butt out.

\N<Item Shop Owner>Thanks to you, I was able to take some really
great photos! Thank you! There aren't many women
who can pull off this bikini armor as well as you.

\N<Item Shop Owner>There aren't many women who can pull off this
bikini armor as well as you. It's not like I'm
charging you a modeling fee, but since you look so
good in it, why don't you take one with you?

\N<Item Shop Owner>I'll make a poster right away and promote it. Look
forward to it!

\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Haa, my heart is pounding... So this is what it
feels like to be photographed in a lewd outfit...)

\CE[79]\CE[78]\C[13]\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(I wonder what kind of feeling the \....\....\.
photos will have...)

\N<Item Shop Owner>Thanks to you, I'm preparing the items that
arrived. Look forward to it!

\N<Item Shop Owner>I'm so excited for the poster to be finished! Just
wait a little longer!

\N<Item Shop Owner>I absolutely love sexy outfits, but that attire is
a bit too much.
